{
  "stem": "13469.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And-- and the conditions, generally, were far worse than in Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was nothing like Westerbork-- it was bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were wooden, three-tiered barracks again, but we had far less room, I would say.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I can't remember that we have heating-- we had heating, as I remember it, in-- in the barracks, and a stove in Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I don't remember that we had that even in Belsen-- might have done.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But generally, the toilet facilities, washing facilities, all those kind of things were far worse.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were reasonably normal in Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in Belsen, for example, the latrines, as they called them, were basically holes in the ground, at best there might have been some sort of wooden framework around it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But that was all, and it was inside a hut, so it was not all out in the open.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But holes in the ground, basically, no flushing or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was a kind of a bath house where occasionally we did have showers in Belsen, but only very rarely.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So generally, facilities were very much worse in-- in this-- our section of the star camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were supposed to be privileged people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were many other camps in Belsen, and some of those were also privileged.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was a camp for diamond people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was a camp for Hungarian Jews, also for exchange.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was a camp for people with neutral connections.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But-- and there was a very big camp for Russian prisoners of war, and we had nothing to do with those-- and many of those died.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And later on, we had a very big camp for women who came from Auschwitz and the camps from the east when the Russian started to overrun that area.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
